text:
A very popular local hawker food centre especially in the day time. Most stalls closed around 8 pm or so.
Affordable cold Anchor pilsener beer at $5/- ( large bottle )  till 9 pm at stall #01-57 Qiong Mei Yuan stall. Run by a polite lady stall holder.
Some say the famous ben Zinger is here, some lum come todai
Cos im homeless tis d only shelter i had
